<% provide(:title, 'Home') %>

<div style="position:relative;">
<%= image_tag("airview.jpg", :class => "welcome_image") %>
<div id="welcome">
  <h1>Welcome to BranPlan</h1>
  <p>Academic tracking app for Brandeis University undergraduates</p>
  <%= link_to "Log In", login_path, class: "btn btn-lg btn-info" %>
</div>
</div>
<div class="container">
  <hr>
  <h1 class="center">Why BranPlan?</h1>
  <br>
  <p>At BranPlan, we aim to provide members of the Brandeis undergraduate community an all in one platform for academic planning and progress tracking. We provide
  a variety of functions for our users, which include but are not limted to:</p>
  <br>
  <div class="card-deck">
  <div class="card">
    <%= image_tag("schedule-stock.jpg", :class => "card-img-top") %>
    <div class="card-body">
      <h5 class="card-title">Scheduling</h5>
      <p class="card-text">Create and customize your current semester schedule by selecting courses in our database. You can integrate your schedule directly into your Google Calendar.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <%= image_tag("search-stock.jpg", :class => "card-img-top") %>
    <div class="card-body">
      <h5 class="card-title">Search</h5>
      <p class="card-text">Browse courses in the Brandeis catalog with our optimized search engine. Discover new courses that you may have never been considered with our personalized suggestion algorithm.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <%= image_tag("progress-stock.png", :class => "card-img-top") %>
    <div class="card-body">
      <h5 class="card-title">Progress</h5>
      <p class="card-text">Keep track of your academic progress with visualized percentage bars for credit and degree status toward graduation.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
